          <a href="${batchUrl}" style="color:#f07d19;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">📋 Open Shortlisting Batch →</a>
        </td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding:4px;"></td></tr>
        <tr><td style="padding:8px 12px;background:#f1f5f9;border-radius:6px;">
